  "contentHtml": "<p>Afterwork Events & Meetups</p>\n<p>Take part in first-class meetups on the topic of AI. Engaging, entertaining and informative presentations await you! Network with experts, learn from industry leaders and discover the future of artificial intelligence.</p>\n<h2>AI Enthusiasts</h2>\n<p>Reach project managers, IT decision-makers, C-level executives, start-up founders, marketing and HR managers in one evening. Position your company as an innovation leader in the AI community.</p>\n<h3>Ø Visitors at our Afterwork Events</h3>\n<h3>100k People Reached with Content</h3>\n<p>%</p>\n<h3>AI Focussed Events</h3>\n<h3>Cities planned</h3>\n<h2>What are \"AI Nights\"?</h2>\n<p>AI Nights is a series of events for anyone who not only wants to understand AI, but also actively use it. Launched in Nuremberg in 2025, we bring together developers, engineers, lawyers, students, marketing and HR professionals – anyone with an interest in technology who wants to help shape the future.</p>\n<p>Our events are 100% AI-focused: showcases, practical demos, interactive sessions. No boring lectures, just a relaxed after-work atmosphere with free drinks and snacks.</p>\n<p>What makes us special: AI is too fast-paced for just a single event. That's why we focus on community spirit – regular meetings where people can exchange ideas, network and learn together.</p>\n<p>Our premiere was already a resounding success: over 50 tickets sold! With top speakers from different industries, companies and countries, we offer high-calibre content for middle management and C-level executives.</p>\n<p>Workshops, sessions and hackathons are planned – and we want to bring companies with valuable products on board who share our vision: bringing people together and shaping the AI revolution together.</p>\n<h3>Event Insights</h3>\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-128.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-128.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-106.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-106.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-107.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-107.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-36.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-36.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-112.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-112.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-34-publikum.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-34-publikum.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-8.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-8.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-113.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-113.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-9.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-9.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-22.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-22.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-20.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-20.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-111.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-111.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-105.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-105.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-104.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-104.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-110.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-110.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-21.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-21.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-35.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-35.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-19.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-19.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-37.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-37.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-31.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-31.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-25.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-25.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-114.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-114.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-100.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-100.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-129.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-129.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-101.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-101.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-115.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-115.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-24.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-24.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-27.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-27.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><h3>Reach out to your target group</h3>\n<p>Our events attract decision-makers from all industries – <br>all with an interest in technology and a spirit of innovation.</p>\n<p>C-Level & Management</p>\n<p>Startup-Founder</p>\n<p>Project Managers</p>\n<p>IT-Decision Makers</p>\n<p>Marketing Experts</p>\n<p>HR-Partners</p>\n<h3>Your Advantages as a Sponsor</h3>\n<p>Maximum visibility and flexible packages for every need</p>\n<h4>Highclass Marketing Material</h4>\n<p>Roll-up displays on site, logo projectors, prominent on the website and all advertising materials.</p>\n<h4>Lanyards printed with your Logo</h4>\n<p>With the largest sponsorship package: All participants will wear your branding throughout the evening</p>\n<h4>Tailored for you</h4>\n<p>Based on your needs, we will develop the perfect sponsorship concept for your company.</p>\n<h4>Flexibility</h4>\n<p>From stands to flyers, presentations, branding and social media – anything is possible!</p>\n<h4>Social Media Postings</h4>\n<p>Your logo on all social media channels, your website and all advertising materials on our side.</p>\n<h4>Digitale Goodie Bag</h4>\n<p>Will be sent by email to all participants – your product or offer directly in their inbox.</p>\n<h4>Showcase your product</h4>\n<p>We would be happy to incorporate your product into the evening – showcase, demo or interactive session.</p>\n<h4>Content for you</h4>\n<p>Upon request, we can create streamlined social media content for your product/company.</p>\n<h3>AI Nights Community</h3>\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-62.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-62.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-73.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-73.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-74.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-74.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-60.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-60.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-89.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-89.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-76.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-76.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-63.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-63.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-77.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-77.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-88.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-88.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-98.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-98.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-67.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-67.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-66.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-66.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-72.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-72.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-99.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-99.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-29.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-29.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-58.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-58.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-64.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-64.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-70.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-70.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-71.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-71.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-65.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-65.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-59.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-59.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-16.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-16.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-127.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-127.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-126.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-126.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-17.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-15.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-15.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-93.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-93.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-109.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-109.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-108.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-108.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-6.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-122.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-122.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><h3>Why \"AI Nights\" Sponsorship?</h3>\nR<h4>Direct access to decision-makers</h4>\n<p>Mid management and C-level executives are regularly on site. Make valuable contacts in a relaxed atmosphere.</p>\nR<h4>Community instead of one-off event</h4>\n<p>AI is too fast-paced for just one event. Become part of a growing community with regular touchpoints.</p>\nR<h4>Appeal through 100% AI focus</h4>\n<p>Underline your importance and show that AI is important to us. By sponsoring AI Nights, your brand will shine in the context of AI.</p>\nR<h4>Many more advantages</h4>\n<p>From social media to digital goodie bags to bespoke product integrations, we'll find the perfect package for you.</p>\n<h3>Event Insights</h3>\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-58.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-58-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-46.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-46-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-108.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-108-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-83.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-83-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-61.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-61-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-91.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-91-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-19.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-19-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-14.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-14-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-128.jpg\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-128-400x284.jpg\" alt=\"AI Nights Nürnberg\"></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-28.jp